sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_048_3_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Reservation of a Connector - Unavailable
    Note over CP,CS: Document Ref: Table 170, pages 145-146/176
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile
    Note over CP,CS: Before: Configuration/Memory/Reusable States: n/a

    CS->>CP: 1. ChangeAvailability.req (connectorId: <Configured>, type: Inoperative)
    CP-->>CS: 2. ChangeAvailability.conf

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req (status: Unavailable, connectorId: from step 1)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Unavailable
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    CS->>CP: 5. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: connectorId from step 1<br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>reservationId: <unique id><br/>expiryDate: <future timestamp>

    CP-->>CS: 6. ReserveNow.conf (status: Unavailable)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Unavailable

    Note over CP,CS: Expected: CSMS accepts the Reservation message with the not Accepted status
    Note over CP,CS: Expected (CP side): n/a
